data.name: Classic Loaf in Sauce
data.description: With real meat as the ingredient, Classic Loaf in Sauce complements any dry food or stands alone as a tasty meal. Made in the USA with the finest ingredients from around the world. Contains no fillers, no artificial flavors, and is formulated without grains (Trace amounts may be present due to cross-contact during manufacturing). CESAR Classic Loafs gourmet soft dog food is served in convenient trays with easy, peel away seals. This single serve, complete and balanced meal for adult dogs makes every mealtime delicious
